# Next.js Patterns

## Route Structure
```
src/app/
  (auth)/login/page.tsx
  (auth)/register/page.tsx
  (customer)/map/page.tsx
  (worker)/dashboard/page.tsx
  api/...route handlers
  layout.tsx
  page.tsx
```

## Data Fetching
- Server Components fetch data via `@/services/supabaseServer`.
- Client Components use `@/services/supabaseClient` for real-time subscriptions.

## Environment Variables
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL` — Supabase project URL.
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` — Supabase anon key.
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY` — Google Maps API key.
